WeRateDogs: Twitter Data Analysis¶

- Suraj Singh Shahi

After going through the whole wrangling process which was challenging yet thrilling, sometimes a little bit frustrating but all in all really challenging and fruitful. As I am here with insightful analysis of the data we just cleaned and analysed. The main focus of the WeRateDogs Twitter account is to show the world how cute dogs are will all their personality and charm and no dog is imperfect that is why the Twitter account always gives more than 10 out of 10 to the humans best friends.

After completing the whole wrangling process we have got 1602 clean rows with 14 columns of data. And to start our Insightful journey let's smile and see the top 2 cutest and the most loved (favorited) dogs.
